{
  "id": "adv_event_2307_01_03",
  "title": "打倒！　\n恋々Poison",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、{user}さん\nめずらしいですね、昼間から事務所にいるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san.\nIt's rare to see you at the office during the day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.247029399900001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "片付けないといけない書類が溜まってまして……\nfranさんは、今日も泳ぎに行ってきたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a pile of paperwork that needs to be sorted out…\nfran-san‚ did you go swimming again today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4558728854,
      "endTime": 12.2827665011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4916099865
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。生放送の撮影まで\nもう、あまり日がないですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. There aren't many days left\nuntil the live broadcast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4916099865,
      "endTime": 17.6032655078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaもコーチの所に行ってますし\nmihoは図書館にこもってるみたいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana is at the coach's place‚ and\nmiho seems to be holed up in the library.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8121089934,
      "endTime": 23.013016033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.2218595185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（『恋々Poison』とスリクスの三番勝負は）\n（三人それぞれ、別の種目で戦うことになっている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The three-way showdown between 'Lovesick Poison' and ⅢX）\n（has each of our members competing in a different event.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2218595185,
      "endTime": 29.646870962500003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんがサッカーのPK、mihoさんは）\n（早押しクイズ、そしてfranさんは水泳だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（kana-san in a soccer PK‚ miho-san in a）\n（speed quiz‚ and fran-san in swimming.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.855714448,
      "endTime": 36.0723809557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2812244412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "星見市の海水浴場は、あまり人も多くないからと\n教えていただいて良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad we found out that the beach\nin Hoshimi City isn't too crowded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2812244412,
      "endTime": 42.2611565587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4700000442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "海で泳いだ後は、髪の手入れが大変ですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though‚ taking care of my hair after swimming in the sea is tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4700000442,
      "endTime": 46.6995466388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9083901242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、ちょっと意外でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I'm a bit surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9083901242,
      "endTime": 50.0706576184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、大抵のことはさらっとこなしますから\nがっつり練習しているところを見るのはめずらしいなと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san usually handles most things effortlessly.\nIt's rare to see you practicing so intensely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2795011039,
      "endTime": 57.566961240299996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.7758047258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ私、器用ですし？\n歌もダンスもステージングもお手の物ですし？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'm pretty skillful‚ aren't I?\nSinging‚ dancing‚ staging – all a piece of cake for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7758047258,
      "endTime": 64.4802489435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、泳ぐのはあまり得意ではないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you're not so good at swimming…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6890924289,
      "endTime": 68.2599314048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.4687748903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "他のことより、ちょっと苦手なだけですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just a bit more challenging than other things!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4687748903,
      "endTime": 71.7995912069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、打ち合わせの後にmihoが調べたんですけど\n私の対戦相手、元水泳部らしいんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ miho looked into it after the meeting‚ and\nmy opponent is a former swim team member.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0084346924,
      "endTime": 81.4283897553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6372332407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "同じく、kanaの相手はサッカー経験者\nmihoの相手は、いわゆる高学歴アイドルです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Similarly‚ kana's opponent has soccer experience‚\nand miho's opponent is a highly educated idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6372332407,
      "endTime": 89.0366208864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2454643719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "『台本なしのガチンコ勝負』は、嘘じゃないですね\nだって普通にやったら、向こうが絶対に勝ちますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The 'unscripted showdown' isn't a lie.\nIf we played it straight‚ they would definitely win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2454643719,
      "endTime": 98.2376411907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、向こうは最初からそのつもりで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ they planned this from the start?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.4464846762,
      "endTime": 101.634171644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8430151294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "ま、『落ち目』のやつらをからかってやろうってところ\nでしょう。……ふん、猫も被り通せない雑魚のくせに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're probably just trying to mock the 'falling stars'.\n…Hmph‚ those lowlifes can't even keep up their act.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8430151294,
      "endTime": 111.8684799503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ひぇっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yikes!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0773234358,
      "endTime": 112.8209288886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0297723741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "――ま、それはそれとして。{user}さん\nちょっとご相談があるんですけど、よろしいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Anyway‚ {user}-san‚\nI have something to discuss with you. Is now a good time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0297723741,
      "endTime": 120.2088197679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺にも出来ること出来ないことがあるので\n無茶は避けていただけるとありがたいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are things I can and can't do‚ so\nI'd appreciate it if you could avoid anything too unreasonable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4176632533,
      "endTime": 126.3587970385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.567640524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "私がいつ、そんな無茶言いましたっけ？\nビジネスの話ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When have I ever asked for something unreasonable?\nIt's about business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.567640524,
      "endTime": 131.80065634739998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.0094998329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスとしては、ライブ以外にも\n露出の場を増やしていきたいと思ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ⅢX wants to increase our exposure\nbeyond just live performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0094998329,
      "endTime": 137.33476075809997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテの頃にやってた番組は\n姫野さんの件で、打ち切りになっちゃいましたし",
      "translations": {
